{"tid":2262273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"朱牧民：誰任總統無礙對港政策！","createTime":"2020-10-29T03:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T02:50:17.000Z","uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d211d01467946fe6aabfa78f3cf33572bc42d3b4","tid":2262273,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"朱牧民認為必須運用政治力量，長遠令香港議題不需只靠某一總統或議員才成功推展。他稱去年通過《香港人權與民主法案》罕有地獲參眾兩院支持，「特朗普原本都似乎唔係好想簽，但因為兩院支持，所以都要簽。」由去年人權法至現時期望為面臨政治檢控在美港人提供臨時保護相關法案，均獲兩黨支持，故即使民主黨拜登被指親中，相關議題相信可推行，港人不用太擔心。<br />\n朱又指，要協助香港不能單靠美國，而是要聯繫各國，認為拜登或在聯絡國際合作較優勝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長文自己上蘋果網睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f35ea4d85c50dce23bddfe4648cc5d2c65664c","tid":2262273,"uid":62714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"比中共回到氣就死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剩係講對港政策無乜意思"},{"pid":"1616d59a6fab0bc92a4f2447c584e73ffc197edf","tid":2262273,"uid":67353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"邊個都得 咁侵侵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81429d7d49d9928698b2049633683a7a1dcfd2ef","tid":2262273,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n唔幫美國drain the swamp<br />\n仲要想死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ecf581afae3d24f37ae3cb3bb56aec99f12e1","tid":2262273,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"仲未瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fd3e23d8f269cbd0405bbdde2479292aba649d","tid":2262273,"uid":115608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:54:41.000Z","msg":"又係啲咩其實侵唔想簽，bipartisan ，點點點<im